TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, IN_PRM_TYPE='TMP' AND SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,11)='$OutputFile', IIF((RTRIM(V_TARGET_TYPE)='Flat File' OR ISNULL(V_TARGET_TYPE)) AND (RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX)='.tmp' OR RTRIM(UPPER(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX))='.XML'),'TMP'), IN_PRM_TYPE='OPF' AND SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,11)='$OutputFile', IIF((RTRIM(V_TARGET_TYPE)='Flat File' OR ISNULL(V_TARGET_TYPE)) AND RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX)!='.tmp','OPF'), IN_PRM_TYPE='TMP' AND SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,10)='$InputFile', IIF((RTRIM(V_SOURCE_TYPE)='Flat File' OR ISNULL(V_SOURCE_TYPE)) AND (RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX)='.tmp' OR RTRIM(UPPER(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX))='.XML'),'TMP'), IN_PRM_TYPE='IPF' AND SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,10)='$InputFile', IIF((RTRIM(V_SOURCE_TYPE)='Flat File' OR ISNULL(V_SOURCE_TYPE)) AND RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX)!='.tmp','IPF'), IN_PRM_TYPE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_PRM_TYPE_PRE_PROCESSING

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,11)='$OutputFile', IIF((RTRIM(V_TARGET_TYPE)='Flat File' OR ISNULL(V_TARGET_TYPE)) AND (RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX)='.tmp' OR RTRIM(UPPER(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX))='.XML'),'TMP','OPF'), SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,8)='$BadFile','BDF', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,13)='$DBConnection','DCR', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,14)='$AppConnection','APP', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,10)='$InputFile', IIF((RTRIM(V_SOURCE_TYPE)='Flat File' OR ISNULL(V_SOURCE_TYPE)) AND (RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX)='.tmp' OR RTRIM(UPPER(V_PRM_VALUE_POSTFIX))='.XML'),'TMP','IPF'), SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,11)='$LookupFile','LKP', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,14)='$FTPConnection','FCR', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,17)='$PMSessionLogFile','SLF', (SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,5)='mplt_' AND INSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,'$$')!=0 ),'MPR', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,20)='$Param_FTPConnection','FTP', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,6)='$Param','SPR', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,8)='$$IPCEXP','EXP', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,8)='$$ParamS','SPR', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,8)='$$ParamW','WPR', SUBSTR(IN_PRM_NAME,1,2)='$$',IIF(IN_PRM_TYPE='WPR',IN_PRM_TYPE,'MPR'), 'ERR'||IN_PRM_TYPE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_PRM_TYPE

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Bei nderung der Foldernamen auf neue Plattformstruktur sind hier nderungen an den Konnektornamen notwendig.
TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
DECODE(TRUE, LTRIM(IN_PRM_VALUE)='BDUDWCR' AND LTRIM(IN_FOLDER) !='BDUDW' AND LTRIM(IN_FOLDER) !='GlobalObj' ,'BDUDWCRR', --Fr NICHT UDW-Projekte wird der READ-Only-Konnektor des jeweiligen steps verwendet LTRIM(IN_PRM_VALUE)='BPUDWCR' AND LTRIM(IN_FOLDER) !='BDUDW' AND LTRIM(IN_FOLDER) !='GlobalObj','BPUDWCRR', LTRIM(IN_PRM_VALUE)='BIUDWCR' AND LTRIM(IN_FOLDER) !='BDUDW' AND LTRIM(IN_FOLDER) !='GlobalObj','BIUDWCRR', IN_PRM_VALUE )
--IIF (V_PRM_TYPE='EXP', IN_PRM_VALUE,REPLACECHR ( 0, IN_PRM_VALUE, ' ', '' )) --IIF(IN_PRM_TYPE='DCR','BD'||LTRIM(RTRIM(IN_FOLDER))||'CR',IN_PRM_VALUE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_PRM_VALUE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: 1 -- IIF(V_PRM_PROJID!='FIX' AND V_PRM_PROJID!='GLOBALOBJ', -- IIF(UPPER(V_PROJID) = V_PRM_PROJID,1,NULL),1) --berprfe ob die eingelesenen Datenstze auch tatschlich zu dem Projekt gehren. Es wird hiermit Vermieden, dass Daten aus csv-Dateien eingelesen werden, die in einem falschen Projektverzeichnis abgelegt sind.

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG) AND RTRIM(V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG) != RTRIM(IN_WORKFLOW)||'.log',3,0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG_NAME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF(ISNULL(:LKP.LKP_CTL00R001V(LTRIM(RTRIM(V_FOLDER)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PROJID)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_BUSINESSUNIT)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_WORKFLOW)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_SESSION)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_WF_RUNINST_NAME)),TO_INTEGER(IN_RULE_ID),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_NAME)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_TYPE)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_FLAG)))),1,0)
-- berprfe ob der Parameter bereits mit dem einzulesenden Wert existiert wenn ja dann gib 0 zurck sonst 1=Insert
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_CHECK_FOR_DUBLICATE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF (V_EVAL_PRM_FLAG=0 AND NOT ISNULL(:LKP.LKP_CTL00R001VCLEAR(LTRIM(RTRIM(V_FOLDER)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PROJID)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_BUSINESSUNIT)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_WORKFLOW)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_SESSION)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_WF_RUNINST_NAME)),TO_INTEGER(IN_RULE_ID),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_NAME)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_VALUE)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_TYPE)),LTRIM(RTRIM(V_PRM_FLAG)))) ,2,0) --berprfe ob der einzulesende Parameter gelscht werden kann, wenn er existiert
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_CHECK_FOR_CLEAR_PARAMETER

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(V_CHECK_FOLDER_PROJ_COMBINATION),'ERROR: FOLDER-PROJECT combination with Folder='||IN_FOLDER||' and Project='||IN_PROJID||' is not valid',NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_FOLDER_PROJECT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE (TRUE, UPPER(IN_PRM_FLAG)!='C' AND (ISNULL(V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG) OR ISNULL(V_CHECK_SESSION)),'ERROR: Workflow-Session-Kombination does not exist for the specified Folder! Please check case sensitivity',NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_WORKFLOW

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG_NAME!=0, 'ERROR: Worklfowlog name '||RTRIM(V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG)||' does not match the Naming rules for workflow lognames.',NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG_NAME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(V_CHECK_SESSION), 'ERROR: Session '||IN_SESSION||' is not defined in Repository',NULL)

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(V_CHECK_PRM_NAME),'ERROR: Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' has wrong Prefix ',NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_PARAMETER_NAME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_OutputFilePRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: Outputfile Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION|| ' for Folder '||IN_FOLDER, V_CHECK_OutputFilePRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_OUTPUTFILE_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_BadFilePRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: Badfile Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION, V_CHECK_BadFilePRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_BADFILE_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_DBConnectionPRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: DB-Connector-Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION, V_CHECK_DBConnectionPRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_DBCONNECTION_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_InputFilePRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: Inputfile Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION, V_CHECK_InputFilePRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_INPUTFILE_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_FTPConnectionPRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: FTP-Connector-Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION, V_CHECK_FTPConnectionPRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_FTPCONNECTION_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_ParamPRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION, V_CHECK_ParamPRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_PARAM_IN_SESSION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_PMSessionLogFilePRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: SessionLogfile-Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Session '||IN_SESSION, V_CHECK_PMSessionLogFilePRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_PMSESSIONLOGFILE_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_MappingPRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: Mapping Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Mapping '||V_GET_MAPPING_NAME, V_CHECK_MappingPRM_IN_REP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_MAPPING_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_MappletPRM_IN_REP), 'ERROR: Mapplet-Parameter '||IN_PRM_NAME||' is not defined in Mapplet '||V_GET_Mapplet_Name, V_CHECK_MappletPRM_IN_REP)

TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_APPCONNECTION_PRM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_PROJECT_PRMFILE_COMBINATION), 'ERROR: Reading Parameterfileentry '||IN_PRM_NAME||' for Project '||V_PROJID ||' is not allowed in Project '||V_PRM_PROJID, TO_CHAR(V_CHECK_PROJECT_PRMFILE_COMBINATION))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_PROJECT_PRMFILE_COMBINATION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( V_CHECK_FOR_DUBLICATE=0, 'ERROR: Current row entry exist in Parameter table CTL00R001T',NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_FOR_DUBLICATE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ISNULL(V_CHECK_FOR_RELATIVE_FILENAMES), 'ERROR: relative pathname ../ found in parameter value. This not allowed! Make use of temp-directory for file exchange',NULL)

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( V_CHECK_WF_RUNINST_NAME=0, 'ERROR: run instance name: '||RTRIM(IN_WF_RUNINST_NAME)||' is not defined for Workflow '||RTRIM(IN_WORKFLOW),NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MSG_CHECK_WF_RUNINST_NAME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
--berprfe ob der einzulesende Parameter bereits vorhanden ist IIF ((NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_FOLDER_PROJ_COMBINATION) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_WORKFLOWLOG) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_SESSION) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_PRM_NAME) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_OutputFilePRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_BadFilePRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_DBConnectionPRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_InputFilePRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_ParamPRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_LookupFilePRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_FTPConnectionPRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_MappletPRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_PMSessionLogFilePRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_MappingPRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_AppConnectionPRM_IN_REP) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_PROJECT_PRMFILE_COMBINATION) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_WF_RUNINST_NAME) AND NOT ISNULL(V_CHECK_FOR_RELATIVE_FILENAMES)) OR (V_CHECK_FOR_CLEAR_PARAMETER=2),
DECODE (V_EVAL_PRM_FLAG ,1,V_CHECK_FOR_DUBLICATE ,0,V_CHECK_FOR_CLEAR_PARAMETER ,2,3)
,3) -- IF return value -- 0=>Dublicate Reject don't write message to Logfile -- 1=>Insert -- 2=>Update -- 3=>Errors Occured Reject row and write message to Logfile
TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION_DESCRIPTION: Ist NULL, wenn der Parameter noch nicht in der Parametertabelle vorhanden ist

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT REP_IPC_SESS_FF.SUBJECT_AREA as SUBJECT_AREA, REP_IPC_SESS_FF.WORKFLOW_NAME as WORKFLOW_NAME, REP_IPC_SESS_FF.SESSION_INSTANCE_NAME as SESSION_INSTANCE_NAME, REP_IPC_SESS_FF.TARGETFILE as TARGETFILE FROM REP_IPC_SESS_FF WHERE RTRIM(REP_IPC_SESS_FF.SUBJECT_AREA) =RTRIM('$PMFolderName') OR REP_IPC_SESS_FF.SUBJECT_AREA LIKE RTRIM(UPPER('%$PMRepositoryUserName'))

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SUBJECT_AREA = IN_FOLDER AND WORKFLOW_NAME = IN_WORKFLOW AND SESSION_INSTANCE_NAME = IN_SESSION AND TARGETFILE = IN_PRM_NAME

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT RTRIM(REP_IPC_OBJECTS.MAPPING_NAME) as MAPPING_NAME, RTRIM(REP_IPC_OBJECTS.FOLDER) as FOLDER, RTRIM(REP_IPC_OBJECTS.WORKFLOW) as WORKFLOW, RTRIM(REP_IPC_OBJECTS.SESSION) as SESSION FROM REP_IPC_OBJECTS WHERE FOLDER =RTRIM('$PMFolderName') OR FOLDER LIKE RTRIM(UPPER('%$PMRepositoryUserName'))

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: FOLDER = IN_FOLDER AND WORKFLOW = IN_WORKFLOW AND SESSION = IN_SESSION
